description: The iBoxx EUR Liquid High Yield 2027 3-Year Rolling Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: EUR-denominated corporate bonds Sub Investment grade bonds only, minimum rating of CCC Bonds with maturities between 1 and 3 years Issuer cap of 3% -On 30th September 2027, the Reference Index will roll into the next maturity window, investing in high yield corporate bonds that mature 3 years later - between 1st October 2029 and 30th September 2030. This roll will repeat every 3 years. -In the final year prior to each roll, the Reference Index will also include Euro Treasury bills with 1 to 3 months remaining to maturity Additional information on the Index and the general methodology behind the iBoxx indices can be found on website ( https://indicesweb.ihsmarkit.com ).
name: Xtrackers II Rolling Target Maturity Sept 2027 EUR High Yield UCITS ETF 1D
